4. Part 4: How Do I Refer a Case?
4.1.	Access the Service Cloud Case. 
4.2.	Complete all of the Case’s Required fields and Save the Case. 
4.3.	Post a Note to the Case explaining the following:
4.3.a.	Why the Case was referred.
4.3.b.	Specifically what information or processing is required from the Referred Case’s Accountable Resolver. 
4.4.	Click the Refer tab. 
